snippet.textDisplay:
I think this video has an incredible hidden meaning.
Not being offensive, but the video tells how we just don’t show mercy over these creatures and kill them to eat them. They have a life too! They are to live a free life! The fact that when the fish saw other fishes being killed and cut, it got scared. When all the people ran to save that fish (even the one who was selling fish) was because Harry was the one trying to help her.
It shows that even if one person could take initiative to do something, eventually everyone will help them.
